definitions.definition: Having a punch ; effective ; forceful ; spirited ; vigorous .
Involving or resembling a punch with the fist .
Behaving or appearing punch-drunk , reacting poorly.
examples: I was so sleep-deprived I was starting to get punchy .

definitions.definition: Of groomed snow : unable to support the weight of a skier, especially when the skier’s weight is all on one ski, resulting in a ski punching through the surface of the snow.
